目标不用谁提要求，球队所有成员，包括媒体，大家的想法是一致的。不用说，大家都会去拼搏，不拼是没办法出线的，但结果如何谁也不敢保证。」 中国足协：李铁执教国足续约至 2026 年"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-e5185532d6893e068527e5176d0fd5ab_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/481598274"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ij/uCwO/skY9SEAMaCDY5MzAzNTE5IOH0hokGMAg4gAJAK3IJNDgxNTk4Mjc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1629637841.9898882", "card_id": "Q_480979026", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 123}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待「工作手机竟然在偷偷录音」，公司凭偷录内容向离职员工索赔 14 万？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据深圳商报报道，某网络公司认为离职员工存在「飞单」行为，要求赔偿经济损失，提交的证据竟是从工作手机中导出的通话录音文件。近日，上海市金山区人民法院审理了这起劳动争议案件，公司辩称，有证据证明李某确实存在「飞单」行为，公司按照劳动合同约定的比例要求他补偿经济损失，合法有据。该手机是公司发放给员工用于工作的，公司有权取得通话信息，所以也不存在侵犯隐私权。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f1a2c18d88c2a48097e499441f16087e_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/480979026"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ij/uCwO/skY9SEAMaCDY5MTY2MDQ2ILPH+IgGMBs46ApALHIJNDgwOTc5MDI2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1629637841.9903696", "card_id": "Q_480707110", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 330}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有什么句子是你一直忘不了的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-3cdd4739cc109316828e5d3edf36191e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/480707110"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ij/uCwO/skY9SEAMaCDY5MTA1MjA3IJqU84gGMAM4ywRALXIJNDgwNzA3MTEweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_fee